# iCloud (custom domain)
CopyArrivalDate yes

IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User APPLE_ID_USERNAME
PassCmd "tr -d '\\r\\n' < /home/aerc/.config/aerc/.icloud-app-password"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
Timeout 60
PipelineDepth 1

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path /home/aerc/Mail/icloud/
Inbox /home/aerc/Mail/icloud/INBOX

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns * !Notes !Trash !"Sent Messages" !"Deleted Messages"
Create Both
Remove Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# Work account (e.g. O365 via DavMail)
IMAPAccount work
Host mail.example.com
Port 1143
User you-alias@university.edu
PassCmd "tr -d '\\r\\n' < /home/aerc/.config/aerc/.work-password"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType None
Timeout 60
PipelineDepth 10

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path /home/aerc/Mail/work/
Inbox /home/aerc/Mail/work/INBOX

Channel work
Far :work-remote:
Near :work-local:
Patterns INBOX Drafts Junk Archive Sent VIP
Create Both
Remove Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
